title: MasterConfirmationAnnexTypeEnum
description: The enumerated values to specify the type of annex to be used with master confirmation agreement governing the transaction.

oneOf.title: ISDA2004IndexVarianceSwapAmericasInterdealer
oneOf.description: The Index Variance Swap 2004 Annex to the ISDA 2004 Americas Interdealer Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement and to the Revised ISDA 2004 Americas Interdealer Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement applies.

oneOf.title: ISDA2004ShareVarianceSwapAmericasInterdealer
oneOf.description: The Share Variance Swap 2004 Annex to the ISDA 2004 Americas Interdealer Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement and to the Revised ISDA 2004 Americas Interdealer Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement applies.

oneOf.title: ISDA2007DispersionVarianceSwapEuropean
oneOf.description: The Dispersion Variance Swap Annex to the Revised 2007 ISDA European Variance Swap Master Confirmation Agreement applies.

oneOf.title: ISDA2007EquityFinanceSwapEuropean
oneOf.description: The EFS (Equity Share Finance Swap) 2007 Annex to the ISDA 2007 European Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement applies.

oneOf.title: ISDA2007IndexVarianceSwapAmericasInterdealer
oneOf.description: The Index Variance Swap 2007 Annex to the Revised ISDA 2004 Americas Interdealer Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement applies.

oneOf.title: ISDA2007ShareVarianceSwapAmericasInterdealer
oneOf.description: The Share Variance Swap 2007 Annex to the Revised ISDA 2004 Americas Interdealer Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement applies.

oneOf.title: ISDA2007VarianceOptionEuropean
oneOf.description: The Variance Option Standard Terms Appendix to the Revised ISDA 2007 European Variance Swap Master Confirmation Agreement applies.

oneOf.title: ISDA2008EquityFinanceSwapAsiaExcludingJapan
oneOf.description: The Cash-settled Open Market EFS (Equity Finance Share Swap) 2008 Annex to the ISDA 2008 AEJ (Asia Excluding Japan) Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement applies.

oneOf.title: ISDA2008EquityFinanceSwapAsiaExcludingJapanRev1
oneOf.description: The Cash-settled Open Market EFS (Equity Finance Share Swap) Annex to the Revised ISDA 2008 AEJ (Asia Excluding Japan) Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement applies.

oneOf.title: ISDA2008EquityOptionAsiaExcludingJapan
oneOf.description: The Open Market Equity Option 2008 Annex to the ISDA 2008 AEJ (Asia Excluding Japan) Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement applies.

oneOf.title: ISDA2008EquityOptionAsiaExcludingJapanRev1
oneOf.description: The Open Market Equity Option Annex to the Revised ISDA 2008 AEJ (Asia Excluding Japan) Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement applies.

oneOf.title: ISDA2008EquityOptionJapan
oneOf.description: The Equity Option 2008 Annex to the ISDA 2008 Japanese Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement applies.

oneOf.title: ISDA2009ClosedMarketsOptionsAsiaExcludingJapan
oneOf.description: The Cash-settled Closed Market Index and Share Options 2009 Annex to the Revised ISDA 2008 AEJ (Asia Excluding Japan) Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement applies.

oneOf.title: ISDA2009EquityEuropeanIS
oneOf.description: The Index Swap 2009 Annex to the ISDA 2007 European Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement applies.

oneOf.title: ISDA2009EquityEuropeanInterdealerSS
oneOf.description: The Interdealer Share Swap 2009 Annex to the ISDA 2009 European Interdealer Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement applies.

oneOf.title: ISDA2009IndexShareOptionAmericas
oneOf.description: The Index and Share Options 2009 Annex to the ISDA 2009 Americas Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement applies.

oneOf.title: ISDA2009IndexSwapEuropeanInterdealer
oneOf.description: The Interdealer Index Swap 2009 Annex to the ISDA 2009 European Interdealer Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement applies.

oneOf.title: ISDA2009IndexSwapPanAsiaInterdealer
oneOf.description: The Index Swap 2009 Annex to the ISDA 2009 Pan-Asia Interdealer Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement applies.

oneOf.title: ISDA2009ShareSwapPanAsia
oneOf.description: The Share Swap 2009 Annex to the ISDA 2009 Pan-Asia Interdealer Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement applies.

oneOf.title: ISDA2010FairValueShareSwapEuropeanInterdealer
oneOf.description: The Fair Value Interdealer Share Swap 2010 Annex to the ISDA 2009 European Interdealer Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement applies.

oneOf.title: ISDA2010IndexShareOptionEMEAInterdealer
oneOf.description: The Cash-settled Index Option/Cash/Physically-settled Share Option 2010 Annex to the ISDA 2010 EMEA EM Interdealer Master Equity Derivatives Confirmation Agreement applies.
